s de constitution et de restitution du cautionnement sont fixées par le marché."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Références"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"  ### Textes faisant référence à l'article"},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Décret n°73-329 du 14 mars 1973 RELATIF A LA REFORME DU REGIME DE LA SOUS-TRAITANCE DANS LES MARCHES PUBLICS (MODIFICATION DU CODE DES MARCHES PUBLICS) MODIFICATION cible"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Décret n°64-729 du 17 juillet 1964 PORTANT CODIFICATION DES TEXTES REGLEMENTAIRES RELATIFS AUX MARCHES PUBLICS CODIFICATION cible"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":"  ### Références faites par l'article"},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"      CONCORDE source Code des marchés publics 99"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"      CONCORDANCE source Décret 60-1044 1960-09-22 art. 1"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1964-07-17 CODIFICATION source Décret n°64-729 du 17 juillet 1964 PORTANT CODIFICATION DES TEXTES REGLEMENTAIRES RELATIFS AUX MARCHES PUBLICS"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1973-03-14 MODIFICATION source Décret n°73-329 du 14 mars 1973 RELATIF A LA REFORME DU REGIME DE LA SOUS-TRAITANCE DANS LES MARCHES PUBLICS (MODIFICATION DU CODE DES MARCHES PUBLICS)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Autres formats"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"* [JSON dans git](ht